  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "In the opening days of the first Damocles Gulf Crusade, the Ultramarines bring war to the Tau sept world of Dal'yth. The daredevil warriors of the Assault Company — among them the glory-hungry sergeants Sicarius and Numitor — fight in the skies, through the streets, and into the Earth caste's testing facilities, chainsword and jump pack against cutting-edge battlesuits. But the brightest stars of the Tau, Commanders Farsight and Shadowsun, hunt the Space Marines toward disaster. Told almost evenly from both sides, this is a clash of doctrines as much as armies — the Codex Astartes against the Code of Fire — and the Ultramarines must master their hunger for glory before it kills them.",
